tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
  station_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_name VARCHAR(255),
  address VARCHAR(255),
  city VARCHAR(100),
  state VARCHAR(50),
  zip_code VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
    station_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    location_name VARCHAR(100),
    address VARCHAR(255),
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_tracking (
    tracking_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID,
    station_id UUID,
    tracked_at TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES charging_stations(station_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES charging_stations(station_id)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
    station_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    station_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    location_lat DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    location_long DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    num_charging_ports INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE station_status (
    status_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id UUID NOT NULL,
    vehicle_id UUID NOT NULL,
    status VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_history (
  history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id INT,
  charging_station_id INT,
  charge_start_time TIMESTAMP,
  charge_end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    total_chargers INT,
    operational_chargers INT
);

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
    vin VARCHAR(17) PRIMARY KEY,
    model VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(50),
    year INT,
    battery_capacity FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    registration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE charging_transactions (
    transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id UUID REFERENCES charging_stations(id),
    vehicle_vin VARCHAR(17) REFERENCES vehicles(vin),
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    energy_consumed FLOAT
);
